{"tid":643255,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人睇完Avengers 3之後，做咗Thanos嘅Fans？","createTime":"2018-04-26T11:21:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-27T14:29:14.000Z","uid":86587,"like":75,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3b6f678eff07b1a1a829323041ed2828c0855573","tid":643255,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T11:21:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://digitalspyuk.cdnds.net/18/03/980x490/landscape-1511973389-thanos.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdigitalspyuk.cdnds.net%2F18%2F03%2F980x490%2Flandscape-1511973389-thanos.jpg&h=6a20d5d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n胡cfu嘅身形，打Avengers一拳一件<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n份人又好有紳士風度，次次打架都係等人主動出手佢先出手，又愛錫自己個女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲要啪完手指之後坐喺度睇夕陽，個樣型到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有邊個都做咗Thanos嘅Fans？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ee8e211b29badb3eb41c7eeadabf08aab39995","tid":643255,"uid":180353,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T11:27:45.000Z","msg":"真男人 有遠見"},{"pid":"1103e270be52ea56c8474ff3a6c7f09f3219e11e","tid":643255,"uid":105567,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T11:31:01.000Z","msg":"同火箭兵團比，邊個魅力四射d？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.tvmost.com.hk/most/uploads/images/2015/Article/2016.10/2016.10.21/5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tvmost.com.hk%2Fmost%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F2015%2FArticle%2F2016.10%2F2016.10.21%2F5.jpg&h=6b8da0c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"201d622e77419ab5ab91dbc49293299c9d7e0d21","tid":643255,"uid":1425,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"1103e270be52ea56c8474ff3a6c7f09f3219e11e","tid":643255,"uid":105567,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T11:31:01.000Z","ms